    %h2 1. Definitions.
    %p <b>&quot;Actions&quot;</b> means the installation of third party applications, completion of specified actions within 3rd party applications or on specific URLs, activation of third party services, participation in surveys, interaction with video and/or audio content, visits to prescribed geographic locations, transmitting messaging, or any other action for which Advertisements provide incentives to users.
